channel.title: RSC Unnamed
channel.description:
[b]Howdy moparscape ;)[/b]
I return after being offline for a pretty long time. The old [i]RSC Unnamed[/i] wich was still in closed beta got pretty much Ruined when i was getting disorganized with my files. So its time for a fresh new try !
[i]RSC Unnamed[/i] was working on a intire new ''Continent'' including mining guild/craft guild/mage guild/Fishing guild etc etc. Also we were buildining a new wilderniss and very nice designed dungeons.
Well.. all i can say is please give me some great idea's while i am starting to work on this project again.
( [b]No we wont change anything inside the game play[/b], we wont add custom items or monsters )
[i][b]1th November 2009 :[/b][/i] [u][b]-[/b] We Are started ![/u]
[i][b]2th November 2009 :[/b][/i] - Design finished for the map time to start working on it.
[b][i]3th November 2009 :[/i][/b] - http://img7.imageshack.us/img7/7484/suggestions2.png ( a screenshot how it possably could be looking soon. )
[b][i]5th november 2009 :[/i][/b] - New map preview [URL=http://img684.imageshack.us/i/ooupdate.png/][IMG]http://img684.imageshack.us/img684/2346/ooupdate.th.png[/img][/URL] [b]- Requesting to give ++ Repu to Hornyhamster ( Ibcrootbeer ) Due he's the map designer not me[/b]
[b][i]5th November 2009[/i][/b] - Banner V1.0 [b] Banner by Reborn ( EndlessLife )[/b] November 8th[ Deleted making new one ] v1.1
